# Test Plan - E-commerce Website

## Objective
To validate the core functionality and usability of the e-commerce website.

## Scope
- Functional Testing
- UI Testing
- Regression Testing

## Testing Types
- Manual Functional Testing
- UI Validation
- Smoke Testing
- Regression Testing

## Test Environment
- Browser: Chrome
- OS: Windows 11
- Tools: TestRail, JIRA, Chrome DevTools

## Features Tested
- Login / Logout
- Product Search
- Add to Cart
- Checkout
- Order Confirmation

## Roles & Responsibilities
- Test Lead: Abhigna Yelleni
- Reporting: Defects logged in JIRA
